{"tid":649213,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大，生日慶祝越唔重要","createTime":"2018-05-01T11:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T14:17:13.000Z","uid":54791,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1c0370a985dd6c33dcafee329a57b6b388264e","tid":649213,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"以前十幾歲嗰陣會好期待生日<br />\n生日一定要買一個兩磅嘅大蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生日前幾日一定要同朋友講<br />\n期待佢地會帶禮物上黎，同自己慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年有兄弟陪自己去op玩<br />\n今年佢唔得閒<br />\n我就靜靜地去下圖書館，去starbuck飲杯咖啡<br />\n只想係呢日放鬆一下，享受下寧靜嘅生活，思考人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到有啲巴打會自己去op玩，自由自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人慶祝?唔緊要啦  有冇人留意?唔緊要啦<br />\n我淨係知呢種感覺好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271b7ecc738dcd33031faabe2fffb48d7975c9fb","tid":649213,"uid":97109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"starbuck飲糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d101d9775c280e65b4e02a2e003fe42f8de96f4","tid":649213,"uid":65686,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"會醒起，但唔會期待。會食餐好嘅，但唔會post出去。"},{"pid":"331ed2a80862d4ab2a5a1720cfcc33e904b11796","tid":649213,"uid":138713,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"這就是成熟了"},{"pid":"ebeed18896c3599e919e584bf0777dbb8b9f150b","tid":649213,"uid":182758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"矯情"},{"pid":"67a915bb6624cce80c3dc1dc596a18b62750e4d6","tid":649213,"uid":42174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"有時會唔記得自己生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb636cf167d33473b8dcc14cbc86